The paper deals with object detection in scanned images of scientific documents, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) techniques such as region proposals and convolutional neural networks. The use of region embeddings and attention models also suggests a focus on natural language processing (cs.CL) and deep learning (cs.DL) techniques. The dataset collection and annotation process may involve information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques, and the use of embeddings and attention models may also involve machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
